# 🧠 4. Quick Root Cause Cheat Sheet

| Problem                        | Root Cause            |
| ------------------------------ | --------------------- |
| Works locally only             | localhost binding     |
| Timeout                        | SG / dependency issue |
| Crash on EC2                   | missing env vars      |
| 504 error                      | downstream service    |
| Works via curl but not browser | SG / LB issue         |

